Package: LAWSHiC
Title: A Package for Post-processing Peak Caller Results
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lingbo", "Zhou", , "lzhou1@unc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package implements locally adaptive weighting and screening approach (LAWS) to 3D peak calling results of Hi-C data. LAWS-HiC improves peak detection by incorporating the locally sptial imformation of the data. 
